{
  "stem": "23942.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, you know, the first time I went to a classroom, and the classroom happened to be half German children, because this was an area where a lot of mixed German and Polish people lived.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was the area, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was-- that area, there was one time it was German, one time it was Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So there were a lot of half mixed, and they were very antisemitic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I remember that I was sitting in the class and they made me feel like I'm a f-- stranger among them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I do remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We had to go to that school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was no Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we-- there were a few Jewish children in each class, and I remember I felt very strange among them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They were blonde-- and not only because they were, but they made us-- I was aware that I was Jewish and they were not.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they made me feel very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't-- and even that thing-- that experience didn't last long, because soon my situation changed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what happened, I was about to go to school, but it didn't take long and I had to interrupt that part of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because then I was told that Rabbi Schonfeld arrived from London, and he was gathering children from all parts of Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and we were chosen, six children from the home, that we will go to London to get closer to the West-- out of Poland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was very important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because my friend told me that somebody was trying to shoot into the home and even, believe it or not, some were trying to kill-- shoot into the home.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In other words, kill a few Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
